type.name: custom

separator.description: character to be used as separator

groups.description: pattern by which input value should be grouped

value.description: Input value if component is meant to be used as a controlled component

defaultValue.description: Default input value if component is meant to be used as an uncontrolled component

onChange.description: on change handler which receives the event with object as a value containing rawValue and formattedValue

onBlur.description: on blur handler which receives the event with object as a value containing rawValue and formattedValue

required.description: Flag to configure component as mandatory
